{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468170/extras/steamDescriptionLogo.png?t=1732151153\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Shaype</i></strong> is a singleplayer fantasy action role-playing game which emphasizes player agency while combining engaging action combat with flexible RPG character progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468170/extras/MainFeaturesStoreBanner.png?t=1732151153\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Player Agency and Reactivity</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Shaype</strong></i> offers multiple resolutions to the problems of diverse characters in a reactive world, rewarding imagination and creativity through versatile player-driven outcomes.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Shaype's</i></strong> combat was designed to be easy to learn but hard to master, testing the ability of the player to problem solve and find openings to strike.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Shaype</i></strong><i>\u00a0</i>features angled melee combat, ranged combat, stealth, abilities, and an in-depth spell crafting system for magic.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Character Progression</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Shaype</i></strong> presents an open-ended progression system which supports the mixing and matching of typical RPG playstyles. Build your character however you wish.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">World</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Shaype</i></strong><i> </i>is set in the inhospitable land of Paradise. Build reputation with the competing factions and settlements that tensely share this harsh and violent land. \u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p c